README.DAS_EXAMPLES

 See pod documentation inside DAS.pm

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

 das_get_dna_to_fasta.pl  - Fetch list of C.elegans sequences and write them to a FASTA file.
 das_get_dna.pl           - Fetch a single C.elegans DNA sub-sequence
 das_get_dsn.pl           - Get list of DSNs for a DAS server


---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

NOTE:

    DAS.pm needs the following packages (all available from CPAN see: http://search.cpan.org):

        LWP - (from libwww-perl) for HTTP communication stuff. libwww-perl requires a number of
        other modules also already be installed. Instructions on which ones, come with the libwww-perl
        distribution. Installation is quite painless :-)

        XML-Parser and XML-Simple - Again easy install of these CPAN modules. Install XML-Parser first.


